2015年6月26日，一家西班牙商擁有的五星級旅館帝國馬哈巴飯店，位於突尼西亞蘇塞市北方大約時公里處的觀光區康大尼港，事發當時有主要來自[[西歐|西歐]]的565名房客入住其中，是旅館最大人限的77%<ref name="update">{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2015/jun/26/tunisia-beach-resort-attack-multiple-deaths-live-updates|last=Siddique|first=Haroon|last2=Jalabi|first2=Raya|title=Terror attacks: deadly gun assault on Tunisia tourist beach – live updates|work=The Guardian|date=26 June 2015|accessdate=26 June 2015|archive-date=2015-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150701105522/http://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2015/jun/26/tunisia-beach-resort-attack-multiple-deaths-live-updates|dead-url=no}}</ref>下榻旅館的旅客和附近的索維亞旅館的遊客在沙灘游泳與作日光浴。<ref name="gua">{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/jun/26/tunisia-tourist-hotel-reportedly-attacked|last=Elgot|first=Jessica|title=Deadly attack on Tunisia tourist hotel in Sousse resort|work=The Guardian|date=26 June 2015|accessdate=26 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150627135711/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/jun/26/tunisia-tourist-hotel-reportedly-attacked|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在大約中午時分，一名23歲、過去曾就讀凱魯萬大學<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.irishtimes.com/news/world/africa/tunisia-massacre-gunman-identified-1.2265468|title=Tunisia massacre gunman identified|publisher=The Irish Times|date=28 June 2015|accessdate=28 June 2015|archive-date=2015-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150702234008/http://www.irishtimes.com/news/world/africa/tunisia-massacre-gunman-identified-1.2265468|dead-url=no}}</ref>、現正學習駕駛飛機的學生，賽義夫丁·瑞茲古伊·雅各比（被[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]方面稱為阿布·亞哈·卡拉瓦尼，Abu Yahya al-Qayrawani<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.express.co.uk/news/world/587095/Terror-attack-tourist-hotel-Tunisia-Sousse|title=Seifeddine Regui alias Abu Yahya al-Qayrawani has been named by Islamic State as the gunman|publisher=Express.co.uk|date=26 June 2015|accessdate=26 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150629192601/http://www.express.co.uk/news/world/587095/Terror-attack-tourist-hotel-Tunisia-Sousse|dead-url=no}}</ref>，1992年生於卡夫鎮<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mosaiquefm.net/fr/index/a/ActuDetail/Element/54042-l-attaque-terroriste-contre-un-hotel-a-sousse-ce-qu-il-faut-savoir-sur-son-auteur|language=fr|title=L'attaque terroriste contre un hôtel à Sousse: Ce qu'il faut savoir sur son auteur|publisher=Mosaique FM|date=26 June 2015|accessdate=27 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150628230828/http://www.mosaiquefm.net/fr/index/a/ActuDetail/Element/54042-l-attaque-terroriste-contre-un-hotel-a-sousse-ce-qu-il-faut-savoir-sur-son-auteur|dead-url=yes}}</ref>）偽裝成遊客<ref name="circ">{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/06/26/us-tunisia-security-idUSKBN0P61F020150626|last=Amara|first=Tarek|title=Gun attack kills at least 28, including Europeans, at Tunisian beachside hotel|publisher=Reuters|date=26 June 2015|accessdate=26 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150629031906/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/06/26/us-tunisia-security-idUSKBN0P61F020150626|dead-url=no}}</ref>，輕鬆地與人交談，接著掏出藏在海灘傘中的AK步槍，對沙灘的遊客開火。然後，他進去旅館裡面，射擊走向他的人。<ref name="update"/>最後他在與保全人員的交火中被槍殺。<ref name="update"/><ref name=Guardian2>{{cite news|title=Deadly attack on Tunisia tourist hotel in resort of Sousse|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/jun/26/tunisia-tourist-hotel-reportedly-attacked|accessdate=26 June 2015|work=The Guardian|archive-date=2015-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150627135711/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/jun/26/tunisia-tourist-hotel-reportedly-attacked|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=BBCNews1/>
